        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And the fear of God was on all the kingdoms of these countries,.... Whose armies were slain, and all other neighbouring ones; for the word these is supplied: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "when they had heard that the Lord fought against the enemies of Israel; and they were afraid to invade their land, or make war with them; nor did the Edomites dare to revolt in the times of Jehoshaphat. ",
